to head off NATO missiles and bombs, install an interim government
in Kosovo that they say is aimed at restoring conditions in the
rebellious province to normal. YUGOSLAVIA-KOSOVO. Has moved. By
Jeffrey Ulbrich. AP Photo PRI101,106. DEL 102
	   ANKARA, Turkey _ About 10,000 Turkish soldiers cross into
