	    &UR; FEATURES: Arts and Entertainment
	   LOS ANGELES _ Pamela Anderson Lee plays Vallery Irons, a woman
who is famous for being famous. ARTS-US-PAMELA ANDERSON. Has moved.
AP Photo LA300.
	   MOSCOW _ Russia's younger generation seems determined to keep
