Peslier, on Sagamix, wins third successive Arc de Triomphe
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   PARIS (AP) _ French jockey Olivier Peslier, riding Sagamix, won
his third successive Arc de Triomphe Sunday after holding off a
challenge by Leggera.
	   Sagamix, at 2/1, took the lead going in to the final straight
after Happy Valentine had lead in the early stages, and won by a
neck from 11/1-shot Leggera.
	   Tiger Hill came in third.
