<SLUG> BC-Italy-Fashion, 1st Ld </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Milan runway offers good gossip and simple styles
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; EDS: LEADS to reflect Schiffer publicist statement Sunday that she
meant she was retiring from Milan fashion shows not all fashion
runways &QL; 
 &UR; With AP Photos
 &UR; By DANIELA PETROFF &QC; 
 &UR; AP Fashion Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   MILAN, Italy (AP) _ The Italian Spring-Summer 1999 collections
just opened over the weekend, but already there is lots to talk
about.
	   The good news is that the Italian designers are thinking simple
for next year's warm weather season.
	   The bad news is that top model Claudia Schiffer announced her
retirement from Milan runways.
	   The non-news, 4th graf
	   (fd)
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
